<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>驗證您的電子郵件</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .content {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-radius: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #ff6f61;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        color: #666666;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #ff6f61;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #ff4a3d;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999999;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer p {
        color: #999999;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
        <img src="<%= locals.logo_url %>" alt="Logo" class="logo" />
        <h1>驗證您的電子郵件</h1>
        <p>您好 <%= locals.member.name %>,</p>
        <p>感謝您註冊我們的服務。請點擊以下按鈕來驗證您的電子郵件地址：</p>
        <a href="<%= locals.verification_url %>" class="button">驗證電子郵件</a>
        <p>如果您沒有註冊此帳戶，請忽略此郵件。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>此郵件由系統自動發送，請勿回覆。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
